site_title: Among Us Dead Body by Wilson Lee

block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: Among Us there is an Imposter!!! I killed my Origami Among Us Character. This is the origami Among Us Dead Body. No scissors, no glue, pure origami, purely origami! And folded from 1 sheet of paper too. Try it out, I hope you like it. Enjoy!!! Here are my other Among Us Origami: Moderato Origami - Among Us Character by Wilson Lee (Heap Art) (No Glue, No Scissors) https://youtu.be/Ib2HcTn_jjs Moderato Origami - Among Us Character Bookmark by Wilson Lee (Heap Art) (No Glue, No Scissors) https://youtu.be/c4hs_9jXnpk Quickie Origami - Among Us Character Bookmark by Wilson Lee (Heap Art) (No Glue, No Scissors) https://youtu.be/T_8rXFCqC-0 Thanks For Watching!
